<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow hero-eyebrow">For Authors Considering a Book</span>
    <h1 class="display-vp hero-h1">
      You're about to write a book that will <span class="display-italic kinetic-italic">outlive most of what you've made.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="lede hero-sub">
      We take that seriously. Straw Dogs builds the one people are still quoting two years later—the one that fills speaking calendars, and opens doors you didn't know existed.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-solid" href="#engage">Start a Project</a>
      <a class="link-arrow" href="#method">See how we build a book ↓</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero { padding: 5.5rem 0 4.5rem; }
  .wrap { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .hero-eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; }
  .hero-h1 { max-width: 16ch; margin: 0 0 2rem; text-wrap: balance; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.4vw, 1.75rem);
    max-width: 44ch; margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .hero { padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem; } }
</style>
